Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.17,1:04:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,මූ
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.93,1:04:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,අනේ නෑ.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.10,1:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,මූ ගමේ නෑ.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.43,1:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,එයා තාම ආවේ නැත්තේ ඇයි?
